```

## Business Rules Implementation

All specified business rules are implemented:

- **Content Authoring**: New content defaults to `draft` status, autosave, explicit publish
- **Playlists & Auto-Assignment**: Triggers run via `runPlaylistTrigger()`
- **Form Builder**: Blocks saved immediately, drag-drop reordering
- **Assignments**: Can edit due dates, no hard delete (mark as `expired`)
- **Users & Organization**: Admins can create users directly with invite emails
- **Certifications**: Auto-issue when required tracks completed
- **Progress Tracking**: Created at assignment creation, cascade updates
- **Activity Logs & Notifications**: 9 auto-generated notification types
- **Knowledge Base**: Attachments via Storage, auto-increment view counts
